<chapter id="design_overview">

	<title>Design Overview</title>

	<para>
		Example is created by three independent services which compose logical
		whole.
		<literal>CallBlocking</literal>,
		<literal>CallForwarding</literal>
		and
		<literal>VoiceMail</literal>
		process incoming
		<literal>INVITE</literal>
		request in sequence and make decision based on certain configurable conditions.
		
	</para>
